  "title": "Senior Radio Frequency Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role Overview</strong><br />We are looking for an RF Design Engineer to own the design and delivery of RF radio modules from concept through production. This role focuses on developing manufacturable, high-performance RF designs that scale across products and frequency bands.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Design and validate RF radio modules that meet performance and manufacturing requirements</p></li><li><p>Develop schematics, run RF simulations, and support PCB layout and integration</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with PCB, mechanical, product, and manufacturing teams through validation and production transfer</p></li><li><p>Support prototype builds, testing, and documentation for qualification</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Hands-on experience in RF circuit and system design</p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of schematics, RF simulations, and PCB design considerations</p></li><li><p>Experience working with cross-functional engineering teams</p></li><li><p>Ability to deliver designs that are compact, scalable, and production-ready</p></li></ul>",
